7/7 If you reached the end of this thread, thank you for reading! ‚ò∫Ô∏è  Just wanted to share my thoughts and feeling behind the video.  #SaveLockwoodandCo #StroudsAppreciation

6/7 For some reason, I think, that these months were harder for him than her, because she left completely alone, with no one to protect her, and he could not do anything about it.  #SaveLockwoodandCo #StroudsAppreciation
5/7 At some point you just resign and leave, accepting the decision of another person and trying not to fall apart. #SaveLockwoodandCo #StroudsAppreciation
4/7 I feel that he stormed out of this cafe because it triggered his insecurities about people leaving and him not being able to protect/keep them around. #SaveLockwoodandCo #StroudsAppreciation

3/7 I think that he was not able to understand Lucy's reasoning to leave - to keep him and others safe. People leaving only brought him pain, there is nothing safe about it.  #SaveLockwoodandCo #StroudsAppreciation

2/7 This song brings for me all his emotions during that time -  sadness, anger, desperation. They live in a world full of ghosts and monsters but the most frightening ones are within our heads.  #SaveLockwoodandCo #StroudsAppreciation

7/7 If you reached the end of this thread, thank you for reading! ‚ò∫Ô∏è 
Just wanted to share my thoughts and feeling behind the video. 
#SaveLockwoodandCo #StroudsAppreciation

6/7 For some reason, I think, that these months were harder for him than her, because she left completely alone, with no one to protect her, and he could not do anything about it.  #SaveLockwoodandCo #StroudsAppreciation
5/7 At some point you just resign and leave, accepting the decision of another person and trying not to fall apart. #SaveLockwoodandCo #StroudsAppreciation
4/7 I feel that he stormed out of this cafe because it triggered his insecurities about people leaving and him not being able to protect/keep them around. #SaveLockwoodandCo #StroudsAppreciation

3/7 I think that he was not able to understand Lucy's reasoning to leave - to keep him and others safe. People leaving only brought him pain, there is nothing safe about it. 
#SaveLockwoodandCo #StroudsAppreciation

2/7 This song brings for me all his emotions during that time -  sadness, anger, desperation. They live in a world full of ghosts and monsters but the most frightening ones are within our heads. 
#SaveLockwoodandCo #StroudsAppreciation
